_sText:
This map is a remake of TimeSplitters2 map Streets, adapted for CSS Defuse mode.

Minor adjustments have been made to the layout from the original TS2 map to help with balance.

Streets is a small DE map for maximum 20 players, hope you enjoy.




If you would like a "Classic" release using original layout, please let me know (only would work for DM - not suitable for DE mode)

*Note this map is not yet full release, work is needed to improve level fidelity and detail - the layout is 90% final
**Note this map is a remake based on the original from Timesplitters series - No content has been ported and the map has been built from scratch using Counter-Strike: Source assets only.
